  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t本来不想搬运，但是看到“李老师”又发了一张图，去拍照留念的人是越来越多。我也很无语，一方面在去年“白纸运动”期间也看到过希望，可是转眼又看到这些人脑子里还是无知愚昧那一套，真的不知道这片土地上的人民到底配不配享有自由民主。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n关键是这地方拍个照还要交20元，交给谁不清楚反正是有收费的。现场有人在监视，而且跟风去打卡的不像是有特别组织的。从下面图中能看到有人说“去贴点福气”，这不仅让我想起了那张著名的网图甘肃兰州人们排队去摸霍去病的雕塑祈求“祛病”，可问题是霍去病23岁就死了简直不要太讽刺。<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTljY2FjNWM1M2QxYmJkOTY2ZjE1LmpwZz93aWR0aD04MDQmaGVpZ2h0PTEyMTY\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e9ccac5c53d1bbd966f15.jpg?width=804&amp;height=1216\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e9ccac5c53d1bbd966f15.jpg?width=804&amp;height=1216\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e9ccac5c53d1bbd966f15.jpg?width=804&amp;height=1216\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvM2QwNzZjN2VjOWY4NmJjODIxZWFlLmpwZz93aWR0aD04OTEmaGVpZ2h0PTEyMDE\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3d076c7ec9f86bc821eae.jpg?width=891&amp;height=1201\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3d076c7ec9f86bc821eae.jpg?width=891&amp;height=1201\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3d076c7ec9f86bc821eae.jpg?width=891&amp;height=1201\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjE1NjU5MDU2YzBhYzQ3Y2M3NjhkLmpwZz93aWR0aD02ODEmaGVpZ2h0PTEyMTE\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b15659056c0ac47cc768d.jpg?width=681&amp;height=1211\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b15659056c0ac47cc768d.jpg?width=681&amp;height=1211\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b15659056c0ac47cc768d.jpg?width=681&amp;height=1211\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYWJkMzhiODg4YjdhZGU3NjAzZjlmLmpwZz93aWR0aD02NzQmaGVpZ2h0PTEyMTU\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/abd38b888b7ade7603f9f.jpg?width=674&amp;height=1215\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/abd38b888b7ade7603f9f.jpg?width=674&amp;height=1215\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/abd38b888b7ade7603f9f.jpg?width=674&amp;height=1215\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNmRkMWI1ODI0MmFlNDVlZWI2MjBiLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDEyJmhlaWdodD0yMDE2\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6dd1b58242ae45eeb620b.jpg?width=1012&amp;height=2016\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6dd1b58242ae45eeb620b.jpg?width=1012&amp;height=2016\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6dd1b58242ae45eeb620b.jpg?width=1012&amp;height=2016\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
